================================
=== Harvester IP Banning Plugin
=== Author: Alec Smecher <alec@smecher.bc.ca>
================================

About
-----
This plugin can be used to ban selected IP addresses from accessing the
application.

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file
COPYING for the complete terms of this license.

Installation
------------
To use the plugin:
 - Create a file on the server in the plugin's directory (typically this will
   be plugins/generic/ipban/ips.txt relative to the Harvester installation)
   containing IP addresses to ban, one per line.
 - As Site Administrator, go into the "System Plugins" page, into the "Generic"
   plugin category, and enable the IP Banning Plugin.


